  "texts": [
    "The most recent literature search for this study was conducted in November 2023.",
    "We employed a range of specific keywords to guide our search (see Appendix 1), including \"professional development in China,\" \"professional training,\" and \"in-service teacher education.\"",
    "Additionally, the search included keywords related to \"teacher education,\" \"faculty development in China,\" \"efficacy,\" and \"teacher efficacy,\" with a particular focus on STEM teachers in China.",
    "To ensure thoroughness, our research process also involved meticulously reviewing the reference lists of the articles we found and existing review studies on the impact of STEM teachers' professional development on teacher self-efficacy.",
    "This strategy aimed to uncover relevant studies that might not have been captured in the initial database search."
  ],
